{"questionId":"19926","questionHtml":"<p>Write down the null and alternative hypotheses for the test.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>Let <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>μ</mi></math> be the mean mass of the melons produced by the farm.</p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mtext>H</mtext><mn>0</mn></msub><mo>:</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mi>μ</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>6</mn><mo> </mo><mtext>kg</mtext></math>, <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mtext>H</mtext><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>:</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mi>μ</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>6</mn><mo> </mo><mtext>kg</mtext></math> only&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>A1</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Accept <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mtext>H</mtext><mn>0</mn></msub><mo>:</mo></math> The mean mass of melons produced by the farm is equal to <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>2</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>6</mn><mo> </mo><mtext>kg</mtext></math><br><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mtext>H</mtext><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>:</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo></math>The mean mass of melons produced by the farm is greater than <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>2</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>6</mn><mo> </mo><mtext>kg</mtext></math></p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Award <strong>A0</strong> if <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>2</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>6</mn><mo> </mo><mtext>kg</mtext></math> does not appear in the hypothesis.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>[1 mark]</strong></p>","meta":{"questionId":"19926","referenceCode":"EXN.2.AHL.TZ0.6c","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Write down the null and alternative hypotheses for the test.","paper":"2","level":"AHL","questionNumber":"c","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 1]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 4—Statistics and probability","Topic 4—Statistics and probability","AHL 4.18—T and Z test, type I and II errors"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}